      <section eId="sec_5_531">
        <num>5-531</num>
        <heading>Brokerage on loans; recovery of excess; effect of restitution</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_5_531__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of section eighty-three\nhundred three of the civil practice law and rules, and direct\nrestitution. Whenever the court shall determine that a violation of this\narticle has occurred, the court may impose a civil penalty of not more\nthan one thousand dollars for each violation. In connection with any\nsuch proposed application, the attorney general is authorized to take\nproof and make a determination of the relevant facts and to issue\nsubpoenas in accordance with the civil practice law and rules.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
